methods.name: createVault
methods.desc: Create the vault with all configuration

methods.name: optInAssets
methods.desc: Opt the contract into required assets and set initial rate

methods.name: closeOut
methods.desc:
User closes out - withdraws all and claims all yield
WARNING: Any unrealized USDC yield (not yet harvested) will be lost

methods.name: deposit
methods.desc:
User deposits USDC into the vault
USDC is forwarded to Orbital Lending for yield generation

methods.name: withdraw
methods.desc:
User withdraws USDC from the vault
cUSDC is redeemed from Orbital at current rate

methods.name: claimYield
methods.desc: User claims their accumulated ASA yield

methods.name: harvestAndSwap
methods.desc:
Harvest accumulated yield and swap to project ASA
Only callable by creator or RareFi
